{"type":"message","id":"20ef89b7","parentId":"8347fb54","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:13:36.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"查询结果显示只有1个session，而这个session正是当前这个定时任务本身（agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978）。这不是与用户的活跃对话，而是定时任务在执行。\n\n让我确认一下，这个session的label是\"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习\"，这是当前cron任务本身，不是用户发起的对话。\n\n根据规则，只有当有最近5分钟内的用户消息时才不算空闲。当前只有cron任务本身在运行，没有其他用户对话，所以应该执行自主学习。\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态\n2. 整理3-5条关键信息\n3. 保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n让我先搜索相关信息。","thinkingSignature":"1ae96158ae7b49b953c8e6c9bd1731f96ac786d74955017e05bd9d60e3c67a41"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到只有当前定时任务在运行，没有用户活跃对话。执行自主学习任务。\n\n搜索道简网络相关行业最新动态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dd3hdsbozcs7_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":862,"output":249,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45092,"cost":{"input":0.0002586,"output":0.0002988,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00187683}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775052808913}}
{"type":"message","id":"51ff70a9","parentId":"20ef89b7","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:13:36.411Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_dd3hdsbozcs7_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775052816407}}
{"type":"message","id":"3dca82b2","parentId":"51ff70a9","timestamp":"2026-04-01T14:13:40.276Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我需要使用 miaoda-studio-cli search-summary 来搜索相关行业信息。让我搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等最新动态。","thinkingSignature":"a74630fdcbdf1ed596d5cb0f6196b856a17d77525ed9e4f977fcc16bf251f982"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_dge85hur9az7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新政策动态\" --output json 2>/dev/null || echo \"SEARCH_FAILED\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1626,"output":101,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45708,"cost":{"input":0.0004878,"output":0.00012119999999999999,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019284299999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775052816410}}
